-- U.S. Treasury's Geithner Says China Will Decide to Renew Currency `Reform'
-- Christopher Wellisz
-- 2010-04-23T22:26:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-23/u-s-treasury-s-geithner-says-china-will-decide-to-renew-currency-reform-.html

          
          
             Treasury Secretary Timothy F.
Geithner said he’s confident that China will decide it’s in its
interest to renew the process of loosening controls over its
currency, the yuan. He spoke in a news conference following a
meeting of the Group of 20 nations in Washington.  
